Package cofh.api.block

(C) 2014 Team CoFH / CoFH / Cult of the Full Hub http://www.teamcofh.com

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBlockAppearance
    Implement this interface on blocks that can mimic the appearance of other blocks.
    IBlockConfigGui
    Implement this interface on blocks which have a GUI that needs a tool (e.g., multimeter) to open.
    IBlockDebug
    Implement this interface on blocks which have some debug method which can be activated via a tool or other means.
    IBlockInfo
    Implement this interface on blocks which can provide information about themselves.
    IDismantleable
    Implemented on Blocks which have some method of being instantly dismantled.
